title: Inside the Parker: Rays Stay Alive; 3 LDS Game 5's; Rob's Top 3 Playoff Teams; Dodgers/Nats Game 5 Preview
itunes:title: Inside the Parker: Rays Stay Alive; 3 LDS Game 5's; Rob's Top 3 Playoff Teams; Dodgers/Nats Game 5 Preview
description:
This week on Inside the (Rob) Parker, Rob previews a trio of Divisional Round Game 5's after the Rays took Game 4 against Houston to force an elimination game, the Nationals/Dodgers, and Braves/Cardinals deciding matchups, He also names his Top 3 MLB Teams of the Week.

Guest: Tim Cates -  Dodgers pregame host looks at how the Dodgers blew a chance to close out the Nationals, and previews Game 5.
